{
  "stem": "8002.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they all hold the rifles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we saw about four or five trucks there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they told the people to take off their clothes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they didn't see yet the graves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So everybody took off their clothes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because if you didn't take off the clothes, they-- they went with a whip and hit them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then we inched over a little closer to the forest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We saw four graves-- gigantic graves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they put the people right by the graves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they told them to stay all on one side, by the graves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then we saw the trucks open the canvas.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And in the-- the trucks had, again, the big machine guns.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And-- and they started to shoot the people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the people were falling in the graves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But then the [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Latvians, ?] the [NON-ENGLISH], took the shovels, and started to shovel the earth over the people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they kept on moving.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So the German officer says, the devils.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They're still not dead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Take-- everybody take the bayonet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And wherever it moves, stick the bayonet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But they kept on moving.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Then he says, again, the officer, the Nazi-- he says, even if you want to kill them, the devils, you can't kill them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then they took big sacks of white sand.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "To me, I didn't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Because I was, at that time, small.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But my mother says, this is lime.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And after they put, in a half an hour, the graves stopped moving.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then they were drinking and laughing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he says, finally we killed the devil.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, I started to walk away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wanted to relieve myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I started to walk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the forest, I didn't realize I walked that far.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I start to look for my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
